Interface SymmetricMeter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OpenemsComponent
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DummySymmetricMeter, DummySymmetricPvInverter, FeneconDessGridMeter, FeneconDessPvMeter, FeneconMiniGridMeter, FeneconMiniPvMeter, FeneconProPvMeter, GridMeter, GridMeter, KostalPikoGridMeter, MeterArtemesAM2, MeterBControlEM300, MeterCarloGavazziEm300, MeterJanitzaUmg96rme, MeterMicrocareSDM630, MeterPqplusUmd97, MeterSocomecCountisE14, MeterSocomecDirisA10, MeterSocomecDirisA14, MeterSocomecDirisB30, MeterSocomecDirisE24, MeterWeidmueller525, NrcMeter, ProductionMeter, PvInverter, SolarLog, VirtualAdd

    public interface SymmetricMeter
extends OpenemsComponent
    Represents a Symmetric Meter.

    • Negative ActivePower and ConsumptionActivePower represent Consumption, i.e. power that is 'leaving the system', e.g. feed-to-grid
    • Positive ActivePower and ProductionActivePower represent Production, i.e. power that is 'entering the system', e.g. buy-from-grid
